XZot1K.plugins.zb.utils.subcommands

Class MainCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • XZot1K.plugins.zb.utils.subcommands.MainCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.bukkit.command.CommandExecutor, org.bukkit.command.TabCompleter, org.bukkit.command.TabExecutor, SubCommand

    public abstract class MainCommand
extends java.lang.Object
implements SubCommand
    A command that can contain subcommands which are accessed by /(command) (subcommand).
    This should be able to be nested into another MainCommand for subcommands in a subcommand.

    You can add your subcommands with addSubCommand(SubCommand)

    The onCommand in this class will never return false unless done so in a subcommand given.
